              <li><a href="https://www.vaughan.ca/sites/default/files/2023-03/158-2019%20(Consolidated).pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">By-Law 158-2019 (Full Text PDF)</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <p>Regulations can change. We recommend verifying current requirements directly with the City of Vaughan before making any decisions about listing your property.</p>

